This map i have created for our Clan ZFC. It's a Zombie Mod Map. I still have to add lights, decals, fix some bugs a lot of props and so on... 
Now it's better looking and a litte bit better designed and i have added props  
You can use it on your Server of course, but if you have any suggestions for the map please send a Email to "OmegaK2[at]gmx[d0t].de"

Map Info:
Size: 1.757.668 Bytes


Spawnpoints: 32 T, 32 CT (64) 
Notes: No lights, not all rooms finished yet, Decals missing
Compiling Time: vbsp.exe 21 sek. 
vvis.exe 40 min.

Get the newer version! http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/20787!
